">英國唔要你呀<br />\n＃７１３４１<br />\n你咪話中囯Ｄ女女除衫求你影佢嘅？<br />\nＳＯＮＹ龍友攝影師？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3088f3557ee4cc12baa913a15c43df3ae13d5656","tid":1521340,"uid":28451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:42:47.000Z","msg":"時代革命<br />\n香港獨立"},{"pid":"3fc503d75b98c0092d0b0ecb5575307e685062f1","tid":1521340,"uid":263349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港獨立 </span>"},{"pid":"64d4a36263c97032cc737ceba9db84c59a5ef479","tid":1521340,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36916feb8c24b053bc76b927bc565f5832581075","tid":1521340,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:49:43.000Z","msg":"根本係一個偽命運。<br />\n<br />\n中国而家國運咁差，只要我哋贏呢場仗，香港只會有獨立一途。<br />\n<br />\n但係而家吹呢個口號，只會有害無益：<br />\n1. 其他人，甚至其他國家出聲幫我哋嘅，都係因為我哋有民主呢個基本訴求，而家嗌香港獨立，唔見得會爭取到新嘅支持者之餘，仲可能流失好多既有支持者（我知係民意論，但係中共大條道理派兵嚟唔準其他國家指三道四）<br />\n2.我哋而家做緊嘅嘢同爭取獨立，本質上無分別，都係先削弱統治權威，後謀對策，現階段唔適合拎個咁具爭議性嘅議題嚟講。<br />\n<br />\n我都希望有一日可以喺香港嘅國旗下同咁多位巴打慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登治國！"},{"pid":"46b38de66d21328e32b50b3bc07d04cca362a5d9","tid":1521340,"uid":63095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f64d1632e06ba5f82edb2ebd7cd2c8a1956fc0ff","tid":1521340,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"希望有生之年會聽到大家嗌香港獨立啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"睇黎你冇去三年前個香港_ _ 集會"},{"pid":"7b571f2ddbec0c6097efc9f82d198601ccdc2761","tid":1521340,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">830 大濫捕 黑警被斬 完全將焦點轉移<br />\n<br />\n提提大家 我地今日出黎目的係<br />\n<br />\n因為5年前831中共就普選設下「提名委員會」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">還我真普選！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日港島見！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Sogo&mdash;&mdash;&gt;遮打<br />\n遮打&mdash;&mdash;&gt;Sogo</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立！"},{"pid":"c5b1d280b991b68633d3f03bef41ec383617a021","tid":1521340,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a6a1a075457b31fa464b5beb70ae8cf012c81b1","tid":1521340,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e7a316666e598718ddc327c8fa1ff142c6a6ba3","tid":1521340,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"今日唔討論獨立，等2047二次回歸啦"},{"pid":"1d422d3178623c8c420b55aa75b21d54f81016e6","tid":1521340,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3535777ddf470a714143dcfe7ef9e805f85bf2e9","tid":1521340,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"無腦既咁尼刻講囉"},{"pid":"79f4567433e8f2ab4f72ef56de1b3ac5c885953a","tid":1521340,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:11:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}